<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Games - Finnegan's Interests</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #667eea;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .back-btn {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .game-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
        }

        .game-card h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .game-card p {
            font-size: 1.05em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .game-card ul {
            margin: 15px 0 20px 30px;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .game-card li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
        }

        .instructions {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .instructions h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .instructions ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .instructions code {
            background: #e8eef7;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        footer {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            border-top: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            .back-btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>🎮 My Games</h1>
        <a href="index.html" class="back-btn">← Back Home</a>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="game-card">
            <h2>📚 History Quiz Game</h2>
            <p>Test your knowledge of English and Medieval history! This is an interactive quiz game built with Python and Pygame.</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-top: 15px;">Features:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ 12 challenging history questions</li>
                <li>✅ Topics: Wessex, Medieval England, Modern History</li>
                <li>✅ Score tracking and percentage calculation</li>
                <li>✅ Instant feedback (correct/incorrect)</li>
                <li>✅ Retake option to play again</li>
                <li>✅ Beautiful GUI with progress bar</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="https://github.com/finnegancreaney/finnegancreaney.github.io/blob/main/history_quiz.py" class="download-btn" target="_blank">
                📥 View on GitHub
            </a>

            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>How to Play:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Download the <code>history_quiz.py</code> file from GitHub</li>
                    <li>Make sure you have Python 3 installed on your computer</li>
                    <li>Open a terminal/command prompt in the folder where you saved the file</li>
                    <li>Install Pygame: <code>pip install pygame</code></li>
                    <li>Run the game: <code>python history_quiz.py</code></li>
                    <li>Answer 12 history questions and get your score!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="instructions" style="background: #e8f5e9; border-left-color: #4caf50; margin-top: 15px;">
                <h3 style="color: #2e7d32;">Requirements:</h3>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Python 3.6+</li>
                    <li>Pygame library (<code>pip install pygame</code>)</li>
                    <li>Windows, Mac, or Linux</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="game-card">
            <h2>🎮 More Games Coming Soon!</h2>
            <p>I'm working on new games to add to this collection. Stay tuned for strategy games, tactical battles, and more!</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Finnegan Creaney | Personal Interest Hub</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
